Two Types of API

SOAP
-> xml based
-> POST
-> using XML Payload | SOAP Envelope

ReST
-> Data format agnostic
-> JSON, XML. images, binary files, etc.
-> OpenAPI Specification (optional)
-> Http Web Methods (Get, Post, Put, Patch, Delete, Options)

Decorator Pattern

- Add new functionality by adding a decorator

Get

- Header
- Query Parameters
- Path Parametes

Post

- Header
- Query Parameters
- Path Parametes
- Request Body
